<item>
            <title>[SPARK-19115] SparkSQL unsupports the command &quot; create external table if not exist  new_tbl like old_tbl location &apos;/warehouse/new_tbl&apos; &quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-19115</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;spark2.0.1 unsupports the command &quot; create external table if not exist  new_tbl like old_tbl location &apos;/warehouse/new_tbl&apos; &quot;&lt;br/&gt;
we tried to modify the  sqlbase.g4 file,change&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;    | CREATE TABLE (IF NOT EXISTS)? target=tableIdentifier&lt;br/&gt;
        LIKE source=tableIdentifier                                    #createTableLike&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
to&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;    | CREATE EXTERNAL? TABLE (IF NOT EXISTS)? target=tableIdentifier&lt;br/&gt;
        LIKE source=tableIdentifier locationSpec?                                 #createTableLike&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
modify method &apos;visitCreateTableLike&apos; in scala file  &apos;SparkSqlParser.scala&apos; and  update case class CreateTableLikeCommand in &apos;tables.scala&apos; file&lt;br/&gt;
finally  we compiled spark and replaced the jars as follow: &apos;spark-catalyst-2.0.1.jar&apos;,&apos;spark-sql_2.11-2.0.1.jar&apos;, and run  the command &apos;create external table if not exist  new_tbl like old_tbl location &apos;/warehouse/new_tbl&apos; successfully . &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;spark2.0.1 hive1.2.1&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="13032773">SPARK-19115</key>
